e\": \"At the time, she also reposted a Story from retired Romanian gymnastSandra Izbasa-Biancacheering her on.\", \"from\": 1012, \"to\": 1116, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1064, \"end\": 1072, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\", \"score\": 0.9997905193716431, \"rank\": 0.00017689455371349536, \"text\": \"Romanian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 1015, \"to\": 1023}, {\"ngram\": \"a Story\", \"from\": 1043, \"to\": 1050}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I hear more vividly than ever the words that the coaches repeated to us almost daily in the training room,\\\" Sandra wrote in Romanian.\", \"from\": 1118, \"to\": 1252, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1227, \"end\": 1233, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandra_Reemer\", \"score\": 0.8441252245272208, \"rank\": 0.1846512365831759, \"text\": \"Sandra\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandra_Reemer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sandra_Reemer\"}, {\"begin\": 1243, \"end\": 1251, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\", \"score\": 0.9997905193716431, \"rank\": 0.00017689455371349536, \"text\": \"Romanian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanian_language\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the words\", \"from\": 1149, \"to\": 1158}, {\"ngram\": \"the coaches\", \"from\": 1164, \"to\": 1175}, {\"ngram\": \"us\", \"from\": 1188, \"to\": 1190}, {\"ngram\": \"the training room\", \"from\": 1207, \"to\": 1224}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"'You, as Romanians, must be more than perfect in order not to leave room for interpretations!'\", \"from\": 1253, \"to\": 1348, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1263, \"end\": 1272, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanians\", \"score\": 0.9953616234783742, \"rank\": 0.003795621629716871, \"text\": \"Romanians\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romanians\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 1303, \"to\": 1308}, {\"ngram\": \"room\", \"from\": 1322, \"to\": 1326}, {\"ngram\": \"interpretations\", \"from\": 1331, \"to\": 1346}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And here, it proves itself once again!\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1387, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Girls, head up and back straight!\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1421, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Girls\", \"from\": 1388, \"to\": 1393}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Keep believing in your dreams!\", \"from\": 1422, \"to\": 1452, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your dreams\", \"from\": 1440, \"to\": 1451}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Go Romania!\\\"\", \"from\": 1453, \"to\": 1465, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1456, \"end\": 1463, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.6928094877976856, \"rank\": 0.44228299452494696, \"text\": \"Romania\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Romania_national_football_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The gymnastics individual final events on August 5, ended in a dramatic fashion after a last-minute inquiry into Jordan'sfloor score resulted in a 0.1 addition.\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1627, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The gymnastics individual final events\", \"from\": 1467, \"to\": 1505}, {\"ngram\": \"August\", \"from\": 1509, \"to\": 1515}, {\"ngram\": \"a dramatic fashion\", \"from\": 1528, \"to\": 1546}, {\"ngram\": \"a last-minute inquiry\", \"from\": 1553, \"to\": 1574}, {\"ngram\": \"Jordan'sfloor score\", \"from\": 1580, \"to\": 1599}, {\"ngram\": \"a 0.1 addition\", \"from\": 1612, \"to\": 1626}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In this case, Jordan's team felt she executed a tour jet\\u00e9 with a full turn better than the judges marked her-they'd scored her a 5.8 in difficulty rather than the hoped-for 5.9.\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1806, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1643, \"end\": 1649, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"score\": 0.9743599826619553, \"rank\": 0.025675769688062657, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this case\", \"from\": 1632, \"to\": 1641}, {\"ngram\": \"a tour jet\\u00e9\", \"from\": 1675, \"to\": 1686}, {\"ngram\": \"a full turn\", \"from\": 1692, \"to\": 1703}, {\"ngram\": \"the judges\", \"from\": 1716, \"to\": 1726}, {\"ngram\": \"difficulty\", \"from\": 1765, \"to\": 1775}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But while coaches can not appeal execution scores, they can appeal difficulty ratings, and Jordan's coaches submitted an inquiry on her behalf-and the judges ultimately agreed.\", \"from\": 1808, \"to\": 1984, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1899, \"end\": 1905, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"score\": 0.9743599826619553, \"rank\": 0.025675769688062657, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"coaches\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 1825}, {\"ngram\": \"execution scores\", \"from\": 1841, \"to\": 1857}, {\"ngram\": \"difficulty ratings\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1893}, {\"ngram\": \"an inquiry\", \"from\": 1926, \"to\": 1936}, {\"ngram\": \"her behalf\", \"from\": 1940, \"to\": 1950}, {\"ngram\": \"the judges\", \"from\": 1955, \"to\": 1965}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The result not only changed Jordan's score from a 13.666 to a 13.766-it also changed the podium results.\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 2090, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2014, \"end\": 2020, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"score\": 0.9743599826619553, \"rank\": 0.025675769688062657, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The result\", \"from\": 1986, \"to\": 1996}, {\"ngram\": \"the podium results\", \"from\": 2071, \"to\": 2089}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Whereas Ana had thought she'd landed in the bronze position, behind fellow Team USA memberSimone BilesandBrazil'sRebeca Andrade, she suddenly found herself bumped to fourth place.\", \"from\": 2091, \"to\": 2270, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2166, \"end\": 2174, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"score\": 0.9085518332709651, \"rank\": 0.0764878672156569, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_men's_national_basketball_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2211, \"end\": 2218, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"score\": 0.9999997088275874, \"rank\": 2.91047737123003e-07, \"text\": \"Andrade\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\", \"Q13474373\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Andrade_El_Idolo\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ana\", \"from\": 2099, \"to\": 2102}, {\"ngram\": \"the bronze position\", \"from\": 2131, \"to\": 2150}, {\"ngram\": \"fourth place\", \"from\": 2257, \"to\": 2269}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But while the result was understandably disappointing, asOlympic gymnastLaurie Hernandezshared during NBC's broadcast, \\\"That's why inquiries happen.\", \"from\": 2272, \"to\": 2420, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2374, \"end\": 2377, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"score\": 0.9999065236799816, \"rank\": 8.561615588276815e-05, \"text\": \"NBC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/NBC\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the result\", \"from\": 2282, \"to\": 2292}, {\"ngram\": \"inquiries\", \"from\": 2403, \"to\": 2412}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sometimes, they do miss it, and they are able to go back and double check.\\\"\", \"from\": 2421, \"to\": 2496, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"check\", \"from\": 2489, \"to\": 2494}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Breaking down into tears after seeing the adjusted scoreboard, Jordan later spoke to the emotional moment.\", \"from\": 2498, \"to\": 2604, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2561, \"end\": 2567, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"score\": 0.9743599826619553, \"rank\": 0.025675769688062657, \"text\": \"Jordan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q3665646\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Jordan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"tears\", \"from\": 2517, \"to\": 2522}, {\"ngram\": \"the adjusted scoreboard\", \"from\": 2536, \"to\": 2559}, {\"ngram\": \"the emotional moment\", \"from\": 2583, \"to\": 2603}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just wanted to come out and do the best I could,\\\" she told cameras following the medal ceremony.\", \"from\": 2606, \"to\": 2705, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"cameras\", \"from\": 2668, \"to\": 2675}, {\"ngram\": \"the medal ceremony\", \"from\": 2686, \"to\": 2704}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have no words-I am just very proud of myself.\\\"\", \"from\": 2